2.00	Richard_Case	Richard Case	Richard Case (born 1964) is an American comics artist, most often seen published by the Vertigo imprint of DC Comics. His credits include pencilling the majority of issues of Grant Morrison's run on Doom Patrol, as well as drawing Jamie Delano's limited series Ghostdancing, the final story arc of Peter Milligan's Shade, the Changing Man and Garth Ennis' the Story of You-Know-Who. Hunter: The Age of Magic with Dylan Horrocks He also did artwork for Marvel Comics Spider-Man, Doctor Strange and Darkhold.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/7/7e/Replace_this_image_male.svg/150px-Replace_this_image_male.svg.png
